---

<section class="notice-section">
  <h2 class="group-title">ℹ️ Notice !!!</h2>
  <p>
    As of February 2026, there is a new group at Google that deals with speech by talking birds and other topics of
    interest for bird enthusiasts, linguists, biologists, animal trainers, or anyone who wishes to explore concepts
    relating to communicating with a talking bird. The description appears below.
  </p>

  <p><strong>Parties concerned and objectives of the ParrotSpeech Group:</strong></p>

  <p>
    <strong>Google Groups</strong>: <a href="https://groups.google.com/g/parrotspeech" target="_blank"
      >https://groups.google.com/g/parrotspeech</a
    >
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>Subscribe email</strong>: <a href="mailto:parrotspeech@googlegroups.com" target="_blank"
      >parrotspeech@googlegroups.com</a
    >
  </p>

  <p class="">
    People interested in the study of spontaneous speech by talking birds. The topics of concern include learning about
    parrot-like birds, speech perception, linguistics, cognition, consciousness, and other topics related to the talking
    birds. To join click on the image below or submit your request to the group by entering the subscription link into
    your browser.
  </p>
</section>

<style>
  .notice-section {
    margin: 20px 0;
    padding: 25px;
    background: #f0f8ff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #000099;
  }

  .notice-section .group-title {
    color: #000099;
    /* text-decoration: underline; */
    /* font-size: 1.1rem; */
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .notice-section .description {
    font-family: "Comic Sans MS", cursive, sans-serif;
    color: #000099;
    text-decoration: underline;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .notice-section p {
    color: #000099;
    font-weight: bold;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .subscribe-email {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .subscribe-email a {
    color: #000099;
  }
</style>
